title: Eldest Daughter Energy
description:
This week June’s in quarantine (again) and Jessica is dealing with true creature feature (puppy). June shares the incredible bonding time she had with her youngest, sick burns and all, and Jessica shares her “girl porn” weekend full of Maritime joy. Then, the gals discuss the importance of “eldest daughters” and Jessica shares some really beautiful Deep Diver messages. Deep Divers, the CDC recommends following all appropriate guidelines for dealing with Covid-19 and Demon Puppies.


 

Visit the Pinterest Board pinterest.com/thedeepdive

You can follow The Deep Dive on Twitter @thedeepdivepod
